Powerful communication moments can change the way we think or inspire us to act. So, which communication moment stood out this year? Nation Newsplex, in collaboration with Jade Communications, invites you to make your submissions of the best and worst of communicators of 2018. Who excelled and who stood out for all the wrong reasons? We will publish the results upon compilation by our team that comprises applied and academic communication experts. Click here for the entry form. Submission deadline: Midnight, December 28, 2018.  